## 🔧 修复工具

### 自动化工具

**代码质量**:
```bash
# pylint 代码检查
pylint app/ --max-line-length=100

# black 代码格式化
black app/ --line-length 100

# flake8 代码风格
flake8 app/ --max-line-length=100

# mypy 类型检查
mypy app/ --ignore-missing-imports
```

**自动修复**:
```bash
# autoflake 清理未使用代码
autoflake --in-place --remove-all-unused-imports app/

# pyupgrade 升级语法
pyupgrade --py311-plus app/

# isort 导入排序
isort app/
```

**安全扫描**:
```bash
# bandit 安全检查
bandit -r app/

# safety 依赖检查
safety check
```

---

### CI/CD 集成

**GitHub Actions**:
```yaml
name: Code Quality
on: [pull_request]
jobs:
  lint:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v2
      - name: Set up Python
        uses: actions/setup-python@v2
        with:
          python-version: 3.11
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: pip install pylint black flake8 mypy bandit
      - name: Run linters
        run: |
          black --check app/
          flake8 app/
          pylint app/
          mypy app/
          bandit -r app/
```

